text: Rachel Anne Sennott (born September 19, 1995) is an American actress, television writer, producer and comedian. She became well known for her roles in Shiva Baby (2020), Bodies Bodies Bodies (2022), Bottoms (2023), and I Used to Be Funny (2023). She played Rosie Shuster in the biographical comedy Saturday Night (2024).
